This paper discusses the challenges of interference management in 5G multi-tier cellular wireless networks, which involves topics related to network infrastructure, communication theory, multimedia systems, and control systems. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.COM (Computers and Society).
